      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The applicant should be a legal nominee or dependent of the deceased worker.\n   1. The deceased worker should have been a resident of the Union Territory of Andaman &amp;amp; Nicobar Islands.\n   1. The deceased worker should have been engaged in any building or other construction work.\n   1. The financial assistance shall be given to the nominees or dependents of deceased registered workers in the event of their natural or accidental death.\n   1. The financial assistance shall be given to the nominees or dependents of non-registered construction workers in case of accidental death only.\n\n",
        "eligibilityDescription": [
